      SOURCE_URL=http://download.rsyslog.com/librelp/
      SOURCE_VFY=sha1:f98e552247ad76b47751d1472fdf1c09b68b8b32
        WEB_SITE="http://www.librelp.com/"
         ENTERED=20080731
         UPDATED=20080731
           SHORT="A reliable logging library"
cat <<EOF
librelp is an easy to use library for the RELP protocol. RELP in turn
provides reliable event logging over the network (and consequently
RELP stands for Reliable Event Logging Protocol). RELP was initiated
by Rainer Gerhards after he was finally upset by the lossy nature of
plain tcp syslog and wanted a cure for all these dangling issues
EOF
